[{"question":"This is 911, what\u0027s the location of the emergency?","answer":"Sandy Hook school.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":4,"aSentId":5},{"question":"OK, what makes you think that?","answer":"Because somebody\u0027s got a gun.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":8,"aSentId":9},{"question":"First of all, let me get your reaction to the release of this 911 tapes, have you heard them yourself and what do you feel about the release today?","answer":"I\u0027ve heard a portion of the tapes, I don\u0027t think the timing is right for them to be released.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":27,"aSentId":28},{"question":"As a member of the family, as a Lanza, have you been able to work out in your mind what on earth happened to turn Adam Lanza into this mass killer?","answer":"It\u0027s been very trying, as a family that\u0027s been shaken to the core.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":32,"aSentId":33},{"question":"How did she seem to you then, did she mention any problems that she was having with her son?","answer":"No she did not, she said her boys were fine and she was looking into the education -- further education for Adam into Washington, you know, they were waiting to hear back.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":41,"aSentId":42},{"question":"What are you as a member of the Lanza Family would you say to the families who lost their children that day and indeed the six adults who were also killed?","answer":"My heart goes out to each and every family that has lost a child.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":45,"aSentId":46},{"question":"Does he give any insight into he\u0027s been coping with what happened?","answer":"Like any of us it\u0027s been a real trial, my heart goes out to Peter, I can only imagine what he is enduring, it was his son.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":50,"aSentId":51},{"question":"How did you hear the news and what was your reaction to when you discovered it was one of your own family who had perpetrated this terrible crime?","answer":"I was at home, I had the TV on only for noise I really wasn\u0027t watching it and I caught glimpse that there had been a school shooting and I thought, \"Oh no not another one.\"","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":56,"aSentId":57},{"question":"How do people treat the family generally?","answer":"For the most part people have been very kind to me.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":65,"aSentId":66},{"question":"You knew her, what do you think?","answer":"No I don\u0027t believe she deserves the criticism that she\u0027s gotten and why do I say that because, until you walked in her shoes as a parent with a special needs child you don\u0027t know what she endured, you don\u0027t know what she dealt with on a daily basis.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":72,"aSentId":73},{"question":"You I believe had contact with Nancy Lanza on the very day of the atrocity via e-mail is that right?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":80,"aSentId":81},{"question":"What did you say to it?","answer":"We were chatting about the boys and he going to Washington looking into some possible school.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":82,"aSentId":83},{"question":"So she was really even then trying to deal with his problems you believe?","answer":"She didn\u0027t relay how bad things were or if they were that bad.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":84,"aSentId":85},{"question":"What kind of a woman was she, Nancy Lanza?","answer":"Well Nancy was a very gentle spirit, a very kind, very giving, very compassionate person, very generous, I always liked Nancy she was a good mom.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":86,"aSentId":87},{"question":"Why do you think she was not able to spot that?","answer":"I guess my whole thoughts on the whole thing is let\u0027s back up to when he was in school and he was labeled to special needs.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":90,"aSentId":91},{"question":"What would you say on behalf of the Lanza family to people like Neil Heslin and the others as they still try and come to terms of what happened?","answer":"Oh, I want to say here on behalf of the Lanza family.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":98,"aSentId":99},{"question":"What do you make of it?","answer":"I respect her for her coming forth and speaking.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":117,"aSentId":118},{"question":"What was that meeting like for you?","answer":"It was -- if felt good after I met with him spoke with him.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":122,"aSentId":123},{"question":"Do you have any intention of listening to it?","answer":"I was aware of what was on most of the tapes or a lot of the tapes.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":137,"aSentId":138},{"question":"Has it gone for you that something that you could possibly enjoy?","answer":"I have to deal with it the same way as I dealt with it last year, you know, it\u0027s -- you can only try to imagine what it is, it\u0027s like to lose a child and unless you -- you\u0027ve lost a child.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":146,"aSentId":147},{"question":"How do you feel as one of the parents about that?","answer":"I don\u0027t think he failed.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":163,"aSentId":164},{"question":"I mean, do you not want to see some legacy come out of this which actually goes someway to try to prevent it happening again?","answer":"I do.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":167,"aSentId":168},{"question":"I was told by somebody down at Newtown that your wife has actually been invited to speak on the anniversary of Sandy Hook, is that true?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":220,"aSentId":221},{"question":"How do you feel as a family about that?","answer":"Yes, it is true and actually I\u0027m praying for Kay, who I know I talked to her earlier today and she\u0027s studying for that.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":222,"aSentId":223},{"question":"What do you say to them from a religious faith point of view, to try and bring any kind of comfort, because it\u0027s clear to me when I speak to some of them now that time has not been a healer yet?","answer":"I think the first thing that we need to say is that God is grieving too.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":230,"aSentId":231},{"question":"How are you coping since I last spoke to you as a family?","answer":"Well, I\u0027m doing the same things that we talked about in that interview.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":257,"aSentId":258},{"question":"When did he finally get this gun?","answer":"A month before he took his life.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":271,"aSentId":272},{"question":"And do you know how he got -- who he got it from?","answer":"He told me that he -- he told me everything and he told me that he have found somebody finally on the internet who would sell it to him and it had to be super encrypted and it had to be, you know, this cool process and he begged me help him because he couldn\u0027t figure out the process and again there are so many -- so many moments of terrible choices with mental illness.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":273,"aSentId":274},{"question":"How do we get to grips with this?","answer":"I think one of the reasons why it\u0027s being hard to tackle is because there are so many guns out there in the first place there are almost as many guns in America as our people.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":284,"aSentId":285},{"question":"What does that tell you about the state of the debate about this everything else?","answer":"Yeah.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":299,"aSentId":300},{"question":"What is the Daniel Plan, how are you going to get me healthier in 40 days?","answer":"Most diet plans are pretty simplistic \u0027cause they only deal with food and fitness.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":327,"aSentId":328},{"question":"... so that\u0027s impressive doesn\u0027t it?","answer":"This one is actually on physical health and -- and actually the reason why is that I discovered that a lot people want to change, make changes in their life but they don\u0027t have the energy to make changes.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":352,"aSentId":353},{"question":"Why should spirituality, the power of prayer, any of that stuff have any effect of my ability to be fit or lose weight?","answer":"You know what\u0027s extraordinary Piers is that people change together in community.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":358,"aSentId":359},{"question":"How are you going to convince people in their heads, never mind anything else, to come and do this because if this is the master plan you got to persuade them?","answer":"So there are a 140 studies now, that say as your weight goes up, the actual physical size, and function of your brain goes down.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":365,"aSentId":366},{"question":"Is that true?","answer":"That\u0027s true.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":368,"aSentId":369},{"question":"When the brain smaller as you get fatter?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":370,"aSentId":371},{"question":"The person with the good brain or the person with the bad brain?","answer":"The person with the good bottle of Jack Daniels.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":395,"aSentId":396},{"question":"Does it matter?","answer":"So start reading the labels, so get on the internet--","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":404,"aSentId":405},{"question":"So tell me what are you hoping, well these audience said, many of them have tried and failed with diets through their lives what is the key take away here from this book that can change things?","answer":"I mean it\u0027s very simple.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":412,"aSentId":413},{"question":"Plant food?","answer":"Yeah, plant food, nuts, seeds, beans, whole of grains--","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":416,"aSentId":417},{"question":"Can you eat as much wings as you like?","answer":"Me chicken, fish, all of those things are foods.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":422,"aSentId":423},{"question":"What are the biggest no no\u0027s?","answer":"Sugar, flour, processed foods, factory foods,(inaudible), corn syrup, trans fats, MSG all these things that are -- the abundant things in our diet that are driving addiction--","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":424,"aSentId":425},{"question":"What do you think has been the most effective thing for you in terms of loosing weight?","answer":"Well there are three things.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":428,"aSentId":429},{"question":"And Rick just a final question for you, obviously you said, the most difficult year of your life, how will you be spending Christmas this year as a family?","answer":"You know, Christmas, there\u0027s three purposes of Christmas.","docId":"131204pmt","qSentId":444,"aSentId":445}]